<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <style>
        .contactsData
        {
            font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, Sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div style="background:white;width:700px;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;">
    <table style="width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td><img src="data:image/png;base64, " alt="">
            </td>
            <td id="fiscalCheq" style="color:gray;text-align: right;font-size: 20px;"><div>%fiscalCheq.label%<span style="margin-left: 5px">%banksAgentName.value%</span></div></td>
        </tr>
        <tr id="fiscalInfo">
            <td colspan="2" style="padding-right:5px;padding-left:5px;font-size:12px;">
                <div><b>%fiscalInfo.label%</b><span style="margin-left: 5px">%fiscalInfo.value%</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table id="fiscalData" style="width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <div id="platTaxNum">
                    <span><b>%platTaxNum.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px;">%platTaxNum.value%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="modeTaxNum">
                    <span><b>%modeTaxNum.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%modeTaxNum.value%</span>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td>
                <div id="operationSpecies">
                    <span style ="padding-left:16px;"><b>%operationSpecies.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%operationSpecies.value%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="formPay">
                    <span style ="padding-left:15px;"><b>%formPay.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%formPay.value%</span>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td style="text-align: right">
                <div id="rroFiscalNum">
                    <span style = "padding-right:10px;"><b>%rroFiscalNum.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 2px">%rroFiscalNum.value%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="orderTaxNum">
                    <span><b>%orderTaxNum.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%orderTaxNum.value%</span>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <img src="data:image/png;base64, iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAArwAAAADCAYAAABxudzKAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAAAlwSFlzAAALDwAACw8BkvkDpQAAABh0RVh0U29mdHdhcmUAcGFpbnQubmV0IDQuMC42/Ixj3wAAACtJREFUaEPt1jERAAAIBCB7m8kqVtIefwx0oLbnAAAglfACABBNeAEACDb3p9hDLTyePHcAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="">
    <table style="width: 100%;margin-bottom:10px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="vertical-align: top;width: 50%;">
                <div id="operationSum" style="padding-right:5px;">
                    <span><b>%operationSum.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%operationSum.value%</span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%currency.label%</span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%pdv.label%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="serviceSum" style="padding-right:25px;">
                    <span><b>%serviceSum.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%serviceSum.value%</span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%currency.label%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="taxSum" style="padding-right:60px;">
                    <span><b>%taxSum.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%taxSum.value%</span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%currency.label%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="txnDate">
                    <span><b>%txnDate.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%txnDate.value%</span>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td style = "vertical-align: top;">
                <div id="receiptId">
                    <span><b>%receiptId.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%receiptId.value%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="salePoint">
                    <span><b>%salePoint.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%salePoint.value%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="salePointAddr">
                    <span><b>%salePointAddr.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%salePointAddr.value%</span>
                </div>
                <div id="operationId">
                    <span><b>%operationId.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%operationId.value%</span>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table style="width: 100%;margin-bottom: 20px;table-layout: fixed;">
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%;vertical-align: top;">
                <div id="recepient">
                    %recepient%
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    <tr>
    <td style="width: 50%;vertical-align: top;">
    <br>
      <div id="sender">
        %sender%
            </div>
    </td>
    <td style="text-align: left">
    <br>
    <div id="rrn">
          <span><b>%rrn.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%rrn.value%</span>
        </div>
        <div id="authCode">
          <span><b>%authCode.label%</b></span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%authCode.value%</span>
        </div>
    </td>
    </tr>
    </table>
    <img src="data:image/png;base64, " alt="">
    <div id="agentInfo">
        <br>
        <div style="color:gray;padding-left:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 12px;">%agentInfo.value%
        </div>
    </div>
    <table style="width: 100%">
        <tr>
            <td style="vertical-align: top;padding-top: 35px;width: 170px;">
                <div id="status"><b><span style="margin-left: 5px">%status.label%</span><span style="margin-left: 5px">%status.value%</span></b></div>
                <div id="repostReceiptId"><b><a href = "%linkRepostReceiptId%%receiptIdNoSplit%"><span style="margin-left: 5px">%repostReceiptId.value%</span></a></b></div>
            </td>
            <td id="contactsInfo" style="vertical-align: top;padding-top: 35px; text-align:right;">
                <div class="contactsData">%contactsInfo.value%</div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table id="controlNumber" style="width: 100%">
        <tr>
            <td style="vertical-align: top;padding-top: 35px;">
                <div style="color:gray;">%controlNumber.label%<span style="margin-left: 5px">%controlNumber.value%</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>
</body>
</html>
